OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fbut drier and brighter weather will
OL,7,Freach Orkney in the morning, then
OL,8,Freach Shetland in the afternoon. Light
OL,9,Fsouth-westerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry end to the day with
OL,12,Fsome sunshine. Shetland will remain
OL,13,Fdry with clear spells overnight but
OL,14,Fsome showers will spread east over
OL,15,FOrkney.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA lot of dry and bright
OL,18,Fweather with light winds. A few
OL,19,Fshowers over Orkney, spreading to
OL,20,FShetland in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
