OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny spells on Wednesday
OL,7,Fwith the odd shower. Dry, bright and
OL,8,Fbreezy on Thursday, perhaps some rain
OL,9,Flater. Sunshine and showers on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
